{
  "texts": [
    "According to my web search, the article by Lester is actually published in the journal Suicide and Life-Threatening Behavior, not the Journal of Family Issues.",
    "The correct citation should be: Lester, D. (2014).",
    "Durkheim's Theory of Suicide as Applied to the Family: A Critical Evaluation.",
    "Suicide and Life-Threatening Behavior, 44(6), 631-636.",
    "The article entitled A Double-Edge Sword is by a different author, Campbell, and it is about the effects of family support on suicidal behavior."
  ]
}